{"tid":2377182,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連詩雅遭屋苑住客投訴貪方便 霸佔訪客車位只為行少幾步","createTime":"2021-01-23T11:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T13:18:27.000Z","uid":146030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"20c79d4266dc1f7f225438f2bdb8e2d0edad4164","tid":2377182,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210123/PYOSVBD4LNETHJ2LVEJO6U3SWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210123%2FPYOSVBD4LNETHJ2LVEJO6U3SWA%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TaudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=e4f07352\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210123%2FPYOSVBD4LNETHJ2LVEJO6U3SWA%2F&h=ed138197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210123/PYOSVBD4LNETHJ2LVEJO6U3SWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n連詩雅（Shiga）與媽咪同住於啟德一號，今日有讀者透過「爆相爆片」向《蘋果》踢爆連詩雅霸用屋苑住客訪客車位，住客已多番向管理處投訴，而管理處雖多次跟進處理，但情況依然未有改善。《蘋果》連絡連詩雅，其經理人代回覆指連詩雅今晚出席仁濟活動時會回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n____<br />\n<br />\n___曾先生斥責：「投訴過好多次，佢（連）都係咁，管理處話會當佢泊時租車位收番佢錢，不過佢（連）係用專用車位證入閘，唔係用八達通卡（訪客用）入閘。」"},{"pid":"eccc1c99009008b13904661c059904b0e12ba44c","tid":2377182,"uid":173695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7088ee14260ef6924e27d08f370e614ee8de232a","tid":2377182,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eccc1c99009008b13904661c059904b0e12ba44c","tid":2377182,"uid":173695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba532203e3bd4c1be62876944e28de60c4364ab","tid":2377182,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim